x4freetext: Most of the targets consisted of self-supporting
rolled metal, 500 to >= 600 microg/cm2 thick, or
material evaporated onto thin carbon or Al backings.
A few thick targets of thicknesses > 1 mg/cm2 were
detectors, 60 to 150 microm thick, placed on opposing
to 40 cm and the solid angles of the detectors were
1.2 to 20 msr, corresponding to angular acceptances
